section: The exclusive purpose of the Venture (the "Purpose") will be IT Development. internet Back office Maintenance And Deployment of medical Service. This purpose may be changed at any time at the discretion of BorrowMoney.com, inc.
explanation: The original text states the exclusive purpose of the venture. The last statement states the purpose can be changed at any time at the discretion of BorrowMoney.com, inc. This contradicts the meaning of 'exclusive purpose of the venture'.

section: Any vote required by the Members will be determined such that each Member receives one vote, however, BorrowMoney.com, inc.'s vote will carry twice the weight of JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go's vote.
explanation: This presents a contradiction because, in the first clause of the sentence, each member gets one vote. In the second clause of the sentence, BorrowMoney.com gets twice the vote. Both clauses happen at the same time, which does not make sense.

section: This Agreement may be amended with the consent of BorrowMoney.com, inc., notwithstanding any objection from JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go.
explanation: The general legal understanding of an agreement means that it has to be agreed upon by all parties. The change means that BorrowMoney.com, inc can change the terms of the agreement without the consent of JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go. This creates a contradiction in the clause.
